author: stsp
msg: Add a new error code to allow ra_svn to signal whether tunnel creation failed.
Use this error code in the 'svn' client to remind users of the fact that
the --username and --password options do not work as they might expect
This is a common question in the #svn IRC channel.
(make_tunnel): If the tunnel cannot be created, raise the new error code.
(sub_main): If tunnel creation failed and the user passed --username or
--password, assume the user is trying to use svn+ssh:// improperly and
